  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-gray-900">What is Mondly?</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-lg">Mondly is a language learning app that has quickly gained popularity for its innovative use of technology. Since its launch in 2014, Mondly has focused on making language learning accessible and engaging through short, daily lessons. The platform is particularly famous for its AR and VR features, which allow you to practice English in immersive digital environments.</p>
  
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-lg">While many apps follow a rigid structure, Mondly allows you to choose the topics that interest you most. Whether you want to learn English for travel, business, or daily life, you can jump straight into the relevant modules.</p>

