  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-gray-900">Key Features</h2>
  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-6 mb-3 text-gray-900">1. Mondly AR and VR</h3>
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-lg">Mondly is a pioneer in immersive learning. Using Augmented Reality, you can bring a virtual teacher into your room to practice conversations. The Virtual Reality app takes this further by placing you in real-world scenarios, such as a restaurant or a train station, where you must interact in English to succeed.</p>

  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-6 mb-3 text-gray-900">2. Daily Lessons and Challenges</h3>
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-lg">Mondly encourages daily practice with short lessons that take only 5 to 10 minutes. There are also weekly challenges and monthly quizzes to track your progress and keep you motivated.</p>

  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-6 mb-3 text-gray-900">3. Chatbot with Speech Recognition</h3>
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-lg">The app includes a sophisticated chatbot that uses speech recognition technology. You can talk to the app, and it will give you instant feedback on your pronunciation and grammar. This is a great way to build confidence before speaking with real people.</p>

