  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-gray-900">Verdict: Is it Worth it?</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-lg">Mondly is a fantastic choice for learners who find traditional apps boring. The immersive technology and gamified approach make it easy to stay consistent. It is especially strong for beginners who want to build confidence in basic conversations. If you are looking for deep academic study or complex grammar, you may find Mondly a bit too light, but for daily practice and engagement, it is hard to beat for the price.</p>

